(53, 1, '2023-12-23 09:58:31', '2023-12-23 02:58:31', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>What is WordPress?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WordPress is a form of open source software, used to create websites such as business information, news, sales… WordPress is written in the PHP programming language and uses MySQL database.<br>Outstanding features of WordPress<br>Installation is simple and extremely fast.<br>Lots of Plugins and continuous updates, you can also write your own plugin.<br>Supports many languages ​​(including Vietnamese)<br>There are many free, professional Themes<br>SEO is very good.<br>Easily manage similar articles.<br>Built-in Latex - mathematical formula editor, you can write mathematical formulas right in the article.<br>Upload and manage images easily,<br>Diverse widgets (created applications) such as Statistics of number of visitors, List of new articles, featured articles, most viewed, most commented, List of categories, List of pages, Articles write by date, ….<br>Managing and browsing Comments is very good, can block spam by IP.<br>Decentralized system with many different levels such as: Administrator, Author, Editor, Contributer, Subscriber. Each authorization will have different powers such as being allowed to post articles, edit articles, delete articles, approve comments…<br>Back up data easily.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Introduce', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'introduce', '', '', '2023-12-23 09:58:32', '2023-12-23 02:58:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/tinhay4/?page_id=53', 0, 'page', '', 0),
